13
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:12,350
♪Igniting hearts, and flames of the heart♪

14
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:16,020
♪Dedication, determined dedication♪

15
00:01:16,170 --> 00:01:18,980
♪Heaven and earth, life and death,
we'll be together♪

16
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:23,550
♪That's a promise that will not waver♪

17
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:26,980
=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:29,860
=Episode 21=

19
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,680
Xiao Yan.

20
00:01:34,630 --> 00:01:36,190
I have a question for you.

21
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,320
Say it.

22
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:41,080
If I had never been to the Xiao Family,

23
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:43,190
and if you had never known me,

24
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:47,830
who would be by your side now?

25
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,080
We grew up together.

26
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,310
Why are there so many what-ifs?

27
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,190
I want you to think about it

28
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:54,440
and answer me seriously.

29
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:55,470
Okay.

30
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,480
Her Highness is my comrade-in-arms.

31
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,720
Zi Yan is my younger sister.

32
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,830
Little Fairy Doctor is my best friend.

33
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:04,870
Liking is another thing.

34
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:07,440
But

35
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,960
liking is for one person.

36
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,080
Isn't liking mutual?

37
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,360
Is liking for one person?

38
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,440
Xiao Yan.

39
00:02:25,670 --> 00:02:28,550
What if Little Fairy Doctor also likes you?

40
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,160
Little Fairy Doctor?

41
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,440
A girl's eyes can't lie.

42
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,190
I can feel

43
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,910
that Little Fairy Doctor

44
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:40,800
cares about you.

45
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,080
Xun'er.

46
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:48,320
I wanted to get angry.

47
00:02:50,270 --> 00:02:51,470
I'm angry at myself

48
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:54,520
for not being there for you
every minute of every day.

49
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,720
I know

50
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:00,440
she is a very trustworthy partner.

51
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:02,670
And I know

52
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:04,270
that love

53
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,390
is involuntary, uncontrollable,

54
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,800
and can't be forced.

55
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,160
I never thought about that.

56
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,590
All I know is

57
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,390
that ever since my father left,

58
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,080
I wondered

59
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,390
about the meaning of being a Dou Practitioner

60
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:24,550
until I met Little Fairy Doctor.

61
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,630
It was only when I saw her
being bullied and used by Han Feng

62
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,000
that I truly understood

63
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,470
that I became a Dou Practitioner

64
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,750
not just to prove myself,

65
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:37,880
but to protect

66
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,390
all those who were bullied by the strong.

67
00:03:41,830 --> 00:03:42,880
It's what I should do

68
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:44,390
and what I have to do.

69
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:48,110
A truly strong person

70
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:51,160
should give back freedom
to everyone in the Dou Qi Continent.

71
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:54,160
This is the true meaning of being powerful.

72
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:01,910
I didn't expect
that you would be so good at preaching.

73
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:04,110
Well.

74
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,600
Did you mean everything you said

75
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:10,080
back in the Black Flame Village?

76
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:11,670
Of course.

77
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,160
Let me ask you.

78
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,640
If I go back to the Gu Clan

79
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,600
and my father never lets me out again,

80
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,640
how will you convince him?

81
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,600
My reasoning won't

82
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
convince your father in any way.

83
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,230
Then you'll never see me again.

84
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,110
I'll do everything I can

85
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,160
to get it from him.

86
00:04:55,020 --> 00:04:56,460
(Subsidiary of Hall of Souls)

87
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,840
I know

88
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,830
you must have entrusted Xiao Yan to Feng Xian.

89
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,830
Feng Xian will definitely

90
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,550
take good care
of your beloved disciple for you.

91
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,830
Teach him Dou Techniques, help him
to participate in the Pill Meeting,

92
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:24,760
and conquer
the Three Thousand Burning Flame, right?

93
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,390
You don't have to waste your time.

94
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:31,510
You can't harm Xiao Yan.

95
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,920
You think you can help him out

96
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:36,560
by leaving him the Bone Spirit Cold Flame

97
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,830
and Flame Mantra?

98
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,920
Yao Chen, you have no idea.

99
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,920
I also gave him a great gift.

100
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:52,200
I planted Magic Poison Spot on him.

101
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:55,320
Flame Mantra? Bone Spirit Cold Flame?

102
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:58,510
As long as Xiao Yan dares to utilize
the power of the Heavenly Flames,

103
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:02,070
he will draw fire to himself
and bring about his own demise.

104
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,320
Mu Gu!

105
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,320
Yao Chen.

106
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,920
You are the one who is about to kill Xiao Yan.

107
00:06:58,300 --> 00:07:00,420
(Pill Realm)

108
00:07:02,490 --> 00:07:05,200
There are quite a few people here
for the Pill Meeting.

109
00:07:05,210 --> 00:07:06,050
Profound Xuan Sect.

110
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:06,910
- Yes.
- Come in, please.

111
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,760
The best of the best.

112
00:07:07,790 --> 00:07:08,990
That's what makes it a challenge.

113
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,600
Eagle Valley.

114
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:11,510
Okay, please come in.

115
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,440
Starfall Hall from Central Plains.

116
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,560
Please.

117
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,040
Here.

118
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,440
Sword Sect.

119
00:07:27,230 --> 00:07:28,070
What's up?

120
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,600
Further along

121
00:07:31,110 --> 00:07:32,040
is the Pill Realm.

122
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,700
Pill Tower is a mecca for alchemists
from all over the Central Plains.

123
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,000
That's why we have to be careful

124
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,720
in this operation.

125
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,600
Especially

126
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,440
if anything happens to you,

127
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,760
not only will it damage Master's reputation,

128
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:48,270
but it will also make all the alchemists
in the entire Central Plains

129
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:49,480
laugh at us.

130
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:50,620
Understand?

131
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,480
Yes.

132
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:52,950
Stop.

133
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,880
What happened?

134
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,880
Yes.

135
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,270
Show me what you've got on you.

136
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:04,910
I have to check.

137
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,000
Profound Xuan Sect

138
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:09,440
came here after receiving the call for heroes

139
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,320
from the Pill Tower.

140
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:13,640
Is this how the Pill Tower treats the gusts?

141
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,160
The Pill Tower

142
00:08:20,110 --> 00:08:21,320
has its own rules.

143
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,790
What is going on?

144
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:26,390
He is Qiu Ling, First Disciple of Xuan Kong Zi.

145
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,350
Normally he is in charge
of the daily affairs of the sect.

146
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:31,040
He seems to be the law enforcement disciple
for this Pill Meeting.

147
00:08:39,550 --> 00:08:40,390
What is this?

148
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,840
What is this?

149
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,470
I didn't expect that those of Pill Tower
were so ignorant

150
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,790
that they even asked me
about the Qi-replenishing Powder.

151
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:51,990
If it is Qi-replenishing Powder,

152
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:53,760
eat it in front of me.

153
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,840
You!

154
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,280
Bring it up here.

155
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:05,550
What's this?

156
00:09:05,710 --> 00:09:07,400
If you don't want me
to embarrass you in public,

157
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:09,400
you better just admit it.

158
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:23,640
What's wrong with him?

159
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,440
This is Taixuan Void Qi,

160
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,880
a special Dou Technique from the Pill Tower

161
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,400
that specializes in suppressing Dou Qi.

162
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:56,870
This is the unique Nourishing Powder
of the Profound Xuan Sect.

163
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:59,710
This item can elevate the efficacy
of a Grade 6 elixir

164
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,790
to that of a Grade 8 elixir,

165
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,960
which is a fierce medicine.

166
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,590
The Pill Tower has long been listed
as a prohibited item.

167
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:12,000
It was an oversight on my part.
I didn't mean it.

168
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:13,910
Please make an exception.

169
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:16,760
Listen carefully.

170
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:18,950
The rules of the Pill Tower

171
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:21,830
are that no one may carry prohibited objects,

172
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,520
fight privately,

173
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,440
or violate the rules

174
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,960
of the Pill Tower during the Pill Meeting.

175
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:32,200
Violators will be disqualified,

176
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,640
cut down on their alchemist grade,

177
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,590
and never be allowed to set foot
in the Pill Realm.

178
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,910
Qiu Ling is a tough guy.

179
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,240
Master.

180
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,160
Everyone.

181
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,840
Today, on the occasion of this grand event,

182
00:11:24,350 --> 00:11:26,350
I, Xuan Kong Zi, on behalf of the Pill Tower,

183
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,910
am here to welcome

184
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:30,840
all of my fellow alchemists
from the Central Plains.

185
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:35,080
It coincides with the imminent eruption
of the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

186
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,200
This year's Pill Meeting
is different from the past.

187
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:41,590
The Pill Tower has issued a call for heroes

188
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:46,150
in the hopes of recruiting talents
without restraint.

189
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:49,710
Regardless of your origins,

190
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:52,550
as long as you are able

191
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,960
to make it into the top ten
at this year's Pill Meeting,

192
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:58,880
you will have the opportunity to take in
the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

193
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,200
This competition

194
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,550
is divided into two rounds of competitions,

195
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:07,280
pill-picking and pill-refining.

196
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:08,910
My disciples

197
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:12,440
will distribute to each of you a pouch

198
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:17,080
containing a map of Pill Tower's treasure,
Myriad Medicine Mountain,

199
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,960
for you to use in the first round
of the competition.

200
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,840
Thank you.

201
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:28,110
Didn't you say there are three heads
of the Pill Tower?

202
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:29,910
Why are there only two?

203
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:33,950
The elder next to Elder Xuan Kong Zi

204
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,280
is Elder Tian Lei Zi.

205
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,400
Another elder is Elder Xuan Yi.

206
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:39,080
The Three Thousand Burning Flame

207
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,230
had always been guarded by her.

208
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:43,480
But it's a pity that during the battle
in the Central Plains

209
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,910
to eliminate the Hall of Souls

210
00:12:46,470 --> 00:12:50,080
fifty years ago, Elder Xuan Yi died after
exhausting her Dou Qi to protect the Pill Realm.

211
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:00,590
One can't avoid his enemy.

212
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:02,550
What's wrong with the Starfall Hall?

213
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,000
You're like a shadow.

214
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:05,670
I see you everywhere I go.

215
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,280
Look.

216
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:11,150
It's the little witch from Wind Thunder Hall.

217
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,350
Make it clear.

218
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:14,910
Who is a shadow?

219
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:18,760
Someone is relying on the eldest brother
of Starfall Hall for everything.

220
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,910
Who is the little witch?

221
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,960
Xiao Yan, who are you calling
a follower of the Starfall Hall?

222
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,080
I am talking about you.

223
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:25,460
You!

224
00:13:25,590 --> 00:13:28,200
Friendship first,

225
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,240
and competition second.

226
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,670
- I have no friendship…
- Competition second.

227
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:31,710
…with the Starfall Hall.

228
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:33,230
No.

229
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,790
No.

230
00:13:36,470 --> 00:13:37,470
Don't talk too much.

231
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:42,880
The first round of the contest
is scheduled for tomorrow at seven a.m.

232
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,590
You will enter Myriad Medicine Mountain

233
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:50,280
to collect medicinal herbs
with the map in your pouch.

234
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:54,790
Arrive at the square before noon to gather,

235
00:13:56,550 --> 00:14:00,320
and the Pill Tower elders
will assess the grade of the herbs.

236
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:03,110
Those who cannot assemble on time

237
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:06,590
or the herbs they pick do not reach the grade

238
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:08,670
will be eliminated.

239
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,110
I hope that you will

240
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,710
live up to what you have learned

241
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:16,080
during the Pill Meeting

242
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:19,470
and seek the honor that an alchemist deserves.

243
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:22,000
- Okay.
- Okay.

244
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,400
What's the best elixir to make
for tomorrow's Pill Meeting?

245
00:14:26,540 --> 00:14:27,550
The higher the grade, the better.

246
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:29,960
Should I use the Doederleinii?

247
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:30,920
Leave it till tomorrow.

248
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:34,140
- Mu Qingluan.
- Let's discuss it at night.

249
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,950
You're paying more attention
to a lover than friends.

250
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,800
Go.

251
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:41,190
Qing'er.

252
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:43,030
Qing'er, listen to me.

253
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:44,350
Xiao Yan definitely didn't mean that.

254
00:14:44,470 --> 00:14:45,310
He just...

255
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,910
Eldest brother of Starfall Hall.

256
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:52,640
Please take a good look.

257
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,910
This is the room of a little witch
from the Wind Thunder Hall.

258
00:14:56,230 --> 00:14:58,320
If you go any further,
people will see you pestering me,

259
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,400
dishonoring the Starfall Hall.

260
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:02,230
I can't afford this.

261
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:03,310
Qing'er.

262
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:04,520
I know you came

263
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:05,840
to this Pill Meeting to win.

264
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:07,440
I can help you.

265
00:15:07,710 --> 00:15:08,550
I can help.

266
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,120
Help me?

267
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:12,280
Why?

268
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:15,550
Others will say I depend on you
for everything.

269
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:16,720
I don't want it.

270
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:18,720
Qing'er.

271
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,470
Just forget about them.

272
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,030
That has nothing to do with us, right?

273
00:15:23,230 --> 00:15:24,760
I just can't take this.

